quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  6,9,"Ne khumukholanga (ye Omurumwa) okhuba malaika, khwakhamukholele okhuba shinga omundu, ne khwakhabakanakaniliye shingala kano kabakanakaninjia."
  6,10,"Ne toto Abarumwa bali imbeli wuwo bakholelwa eshiyenyameno. Ne balia abakhola omubayo mubo, kalia akabakholelanga eshiyenyameno nikababotokhana."
  6,11,"Boola mbu, “Chende khushialo mana mulole indukho yabandu abayingani yali irie?”"
  6,12,"Boola mbu; “Ni bia wina ebili mwikulu nende khushialo?” Boola mbu; “Ni bia Nyasaye.” Yelachilisia Omwene okhubakholela tsimbabaasi. Toto bwene alibakhung’asia khulwa inyanga yeyindukho, inyanga ibulamwo obukanakani tawe. Ne balia abereetsanga mukhusikha, shibasuubilanga tawe."
  6,13,"Ne nebibie bioosi ebiyenzelanga eshilo nende eshitere. Naye niye Omuwulili po, Omumanyi muno."
  6,14,"Boola mbu; “Ekhole owulali Nyasaye, Omulonji welikulu nende eshialo okhuba omulina wanje, ne Nyasaye alisinjia ne shalisibungwa tawe?” Boola mbu; “Toto esie ndalomesibwa mbu embe wokhuranga mubalia abelekhulila Nyasaye (abasilima). (Ne nembilwa mbu); “Olaba kata hatiti mubalia abatsokasinjia Nyasaye tawe.”"
  6,15,"Boola mbu; “Esie eritsanga eshinyasio shie inyanga ikhongo, nikali mbu eloba Nyasaye wanje Omulesi.”"
  6,16,"Ulia uliyinilibwayo eshinyasio esho inyanga eyo, toto (Nyasaye) aliba namuhelesiye tsimbabaasi. Ne okho nikho okhubura okhukhongo."
  6,17,"Ne Nyasaye nakhutila khububii, abulao yesiyesi owulali ye unyala okhubuyiniaho tawe. Ne nakhutila khubulayi (abulaho yesiyesi owulali ye, unyala okhubuyiniakhwo, Ye ni Omunyali muno wa buli eshindu."
  6,18,"Naye niye Omushili owuli hekulu wa abasumba bebe boosi. Naye niye Owamachesi muno, owuli nende amakhuwa koosi."